          <hi>
            <placeName key="Luzern (Stadt)">Luzern</placeName>
          </hi> d. <date when="1877-09-12">12 <choice><abbr><hi>Sept</hi>.</abbr><expan>September</expan></choice> 1877</date>.</p>
